Nigerians are still reeling in shock at the prospect that a Christian like Nollywood Actor Yul Edochie has a second wife and even came to flaunt it on social media. His actions caught the attention of relationship expert Blessing CEO who said just now on her Instagram page, “I respect men who own Up to their shit. I respect yul edochie. His audacity for me.”
